Spoon egg yolks into a bowl. Add cream cheese, mayonnaise, and garlic powder; mix well. Fold 3 crumbled slices of bacon and jalapeno pepper into egg yolk mixture; season with salt and pepper. Fill each egg white half with egg yolk filling. Sprinkle remaining crumbled bacon over filling and top with paprika. Chill in refrigerator for about 1 hour before serving.